This animated book silently flits about as it helps visitors find what they seek.
Working on laying some building foundations...
A shovel is ideal for moving quantities of dirt from one location to another.  Other uses are possible, of course.
The Fort Cystana Silver Dragon guards serve and protect the people, acting as the first line of defense against would-be villains and criminals.

Value.value: We'll work on developing this district soon enough. The others are our priority.

Value.value: Keeping an eye out 'ere. Ye watch ye back. Never know what might come out o' those trees up north.

The Fort Cystana Rangers are an elite branch of the Silver Dragons whom boast great skill in archery, tracking, and scouting. With the potential threats lurking in the wilderness surrounding Fort Cystana, they play a vital role in keeping the people safe.

Value.value: Insanity aside... I prefer this to having our backs to that forest.

value.0: The Mage Guard are a small but well-trained force of growing number within Fort Cystana. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently alongside the Silver Dragons under the command of the Magister.
Set into a copper band is a single green eye, constantly scanning the area and blinking now and then.  When the eye spots something, a faint tingle can be felt in the ring finger.

Love magic for itself. Do not treat it just as a weapon to reshape the world to your will. True wisdom is knowing when not to use magic. Strive to use magic less as your powers develop, for often the threat or promise of its use outsripes its actual performance.

Magic is Art, the Gift of the Lady, and those who wield it are privileged in the extreme. Conduct yourself humbly, not proudly, while being mindful of this. Use the Art deftly and efficiently, not carelessly and recklessly. Seek always to learn and create new magic.
